, 255);\">\n    \n    洞内形态各异的雕塑和古淘金器具向游客讲解了诸多淘金文化和历史，让游客在游览的同时受益匪浅。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <br/></p><div id=\"img53303030\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"53303030|2569650\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"53303030\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"53303030|36483328\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"http://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M09/A8/FB/CggYHVXr4uyAbKbgAAsKTP4wY00420_C_671_10000.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M09/A8/FB/CggYHVXr4uyAbKbgAAsKTP4wY00420_C_671_10000.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5) 50% 50% no-repeat;\" height=\"1192\" width=\"671\"/></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &#39;Droid Sans&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; m