29360|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: auto; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg01.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M04/16/99/CggYG1XfIyGAfF-kAAqxV86BZDU601_R_10000_500.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg01.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M04/16/99/CggYG1XfIyGAfF-kAAqxV86BZDU601_R_10000_500.jpg\" height=\"500\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px;\"/><p class=\"description\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 10px 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">杨家浴场旁边就是洪家浴场</p><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"g_sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>赶海</p></div></div><div id=\"poi4497011\" class=\"poi_title\" title=\"山海关，山海关\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px; line-height: 35px; padding: 30px 0px 10px;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 32px; height: 35px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 10px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0px -81px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>山海关<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 8px; height: 35px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -162px -115px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></div><div class=\"img_box\" style=\"width: 850px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><div id=\"img52728835\" class=\"w_img \" data-likeid=\"52728835|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52728835\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52728835|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: auto; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M0B/18/A4/CggYHVXfHYSAd-tFABS1yxewlJo358_R_710_10000.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M0B/18/A4/CggYHVXfHYSAd-tFABS1yxewlJo358_R_710_10000.jpg\" height=\"399\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px;\"/><p class=\"description\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 10px 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">洪武十四年（公元1381年）筑城建关设卫，因其依山襟海，故名山海关。清乾隆二年（1737），撤卫置临榆县，为县治所在地。新中国成立前后，先后设秦榆市（今秦皇岛市）山海关办事处、辽西省（今辽宁省）山海关市。1952年11月，山海关市划归河北省。1953年，撤市改称秦皇岛市山海关区，至今。</p><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>山海关<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -330px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></p></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 30px; word-break: break-all;\">山海关门票；60，用时2小时。停车费；10元<br/>交通；从东戴河沿着滨海大道30分钟就到，非常方便<br/><br/>山海关：<br/>山海关是秦皇岛市的一个辖区，位于河北省秦皇岛市东北15公里。明长城的东北关隘之一，境内长城26公里。山海关的城池，周长约6公里，是一座小城，整个城池与长城相连，以城为关。城高14米，厚7米。全城有四座主要城门，并有多种古代的防御建筑，是一座防御体系比较完整的城关，有“天下第一关”之称。以威武雄壮的“天下第一关”箭楼为主体，辅以靖边楼。临闾楼。牧营楼、威远堂、瓮城，东罗城、长城博物馆等长城建筑，向游客展示了中国古代城防建筑风格。山<br/>海关是一座文化古城，明代城墙建筑基本完好，主要街道和小巷，大部保留原样，特别是保存众多的仍有一批四合院民居使得古城更加典雅古朴。使古城最为增色的是关城东门。<br/><br/>天下第一关城楼，耸立长城之上，雄视四野。登上城楼二楼，可俯视山海关城全貌及关外的原野。北望，遥见角山长城的雄姿；南边的大海也朦胧可见。天下第一关城楼南北，还有靖边楼、牧营楼和临闾楼等建筑。漫步在万里长城之上，会使你感受到我们祖先的伟大和炎黄子孙的非凡智慧。山海关城楼“天下第一关”匾额真匾，在日本侵华时被抢运到日本，现在的匾额是后来仿制的。</p><div class=\"img_box\" style=\"width: 850px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><div id=\"img52729606\" class=\"w_img img_divide img_fl\" data-likeid=\"52729606|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52729606\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52729606|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 420px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; float: left; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M00/0F/EB/CggYGlXfJSqAH2joABgILxHgH-Y282_C_350_234.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M00/0F/EB/CggYGlXfJSqAH2joABgILxHgH-Y282_C_350_234.jpg\" height=\"234\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px; height: 280px;\"/><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>山海关<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -330px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></p></div><div id=\"img52729123\" class=\"w_img img_divide img_fr\" data-likeid=\"52729123|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52729123\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52729123|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 420px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; float: right; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M04/18/D0/CggYHlXfJgiAO73fABp90TSF4E8868_C_350_234.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M04/18/D0/CggYHlXfJgiAO73fABp90TSF4E8868_C_350_234.jpg\" height=\"234\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px; height: 280px;\"/><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>山海关<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -330px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></p></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 30px; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;山海关古称榆关，也作渝关，又名临闾关，明朝洪武十四年（1381年），中山王徐达奉命修永平、界岭等关，在此地创建山海关，因其北倚燕山，南连渤海，故得名山海关。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;在1990年以前山海关被认为是明长城东端起点，有“天下第一关”之称。与万里之外的嘉峪关遥相呼应，闻名天下。山海关城，周长约4公里，与长城相连，以城为关，城高14米，厚7米，有四座主要城门，多种防御建筑。墙一边是辽宁，一边是河北。其实山海关的主要修建目的是防御满人，所以到了清朝也就没什么实际意义了。</p><div class=\"img_box\" style=\"width: 850px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><div id=\"img52730337\" class=\"w_img \" data-likeid=\"52730337|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52730337\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52730337|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: auto; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M06/18/CC/CggYHlXfJYKABR4sABai0F50re8658_R_10000_500.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M06/18/CC/CggYHlXfJYKABR4sABai0F50re8658_R_10000_500.jpg\" height=\"500\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px;\"/><p class=\"description\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 10px 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">这个景点不太好，居然不让我进，我只好在门口拍张照了</p><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>山海关<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -330px -16px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span></p></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 30px; word-break: break-all;\">海关景区内名胜古迹荟萃、风光旖旎、气候宜人，是著名的历史文化古城和旅游避暑胜地，区内有开发和观赏价值的名胜古迹达90多处。2000年，山海关景区被评为第一批4A级旅游景区；2001年，国务院下文将秦皇岛市山海关区正式列为国家历史文化名城山海关旅游景区以长城为主线，形成了“老龙头”、“孟姜女庙”、“角山”、“天下第一关”、“长寿山”、“燕塞湖”六大风景区，全部对中外游客开放，是国内外著名的旅游区。其中：山海关长城汇聚了中国古长城之精华。明万里长城的东起点老龙头，长城与大海交汇，碧海金沙，天开海岳，气势磅礴，驰名中外的“天下第一关”雄关高耸，素有“京师屏翰、辽左咽喉”之称；角山长城蜿蜒，烽台险峻、风景如画，这里“榆关八景”中的“山寺雨晴，瑞莲捧日”及奇妙的“栖贤佛光”，吸引了众多的游客。</p><div class=\"img_box\" style=\"width: 850px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><div id=\"img52729706\" class=\"w_img img_divide img_fl\" data-likeid=\"52729706|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52729706\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52729706|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 420px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; float: left; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg03.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M0B/18/E6/CggYHVXfJduAVBfKABbn7HGd1x0473_C_350_234.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg03.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M0B/18/E6/CggYHVXfJduAVBfKABbn7HGd1x0473_C_350_234.jpg\" height=\"234\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px; height: 280px;\"/><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>山海关<span class=\"decoration