存粮库、伙房、水井房、碾房、兵器室、练功房、炮室、刑具展室、驻军室、佛室、关公和山神祭拜室等洞室。暗道中既可以囤兵，又可以从内城突发奇兵至攻城之敌后部，如神兵天降一般。暗道中可以驻扎约2000人，洞内设计了排水系统和通风孔，以保证驻扎在洞室中的士兵活动自由，洞内的水井清澈见底，水质甘甜清冽，可供2000余人饮用。</p><div class=\"img_box\" style=\"width: 850px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><div id=\"img52728892\" class=\"w_img img_divide img_fl\" data-likeid=\"52728892|2545935\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"52728892\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"52728892|29748132\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 10px 0px 0px; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 420px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px; float: left; background-image: url(http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424);\"><img data-original=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M07/16/65/CggYG1XfHcKAC9sTAAlGq9AeSag789_C_350_234.jpg\" src=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M07/16/65/CggYG1XfHcKAC9sTAAlGq9AeSag789_C_350_234.jpg\" height=\"234\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px; height: 280px;\"/><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: -249px 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"></span>九门口水上长城<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background-image: url(&quot;http://pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;); background