('20','0','19','[回顾]九龙潭自驾一日游','','','','一起流年','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    \n    8月8日车加车俱乐部来了场【九龙潭自驾一日游】，不但有景可看，还有宝贝可寻，单个奖品价值200元-300元，总价值超过1000元。活动好不好玩，看大家的笑脸就知道了~\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n            <img src=\"/uploads/2016/0331/72fb3c9f439cfae7c9820e65ef273ea5.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    \n    　　感谢参加活动的会员，谢谢你们对车加车的信任；也感谢提供奖品的各单位，谢谢你们对车加车的支持。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">    　　好啦，不再多说其它，咱们看看这次活动的照片。\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">更多图片加自驾群查看，群号：285381306&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    集合在华林国际门口，认准旗子！\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/84451448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; \"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    看！我们的车标！！\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/28881448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    签到时的场景\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/89071448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    准备出发喽~~\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/60401448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    大合影~拍照时旁边很多围观者*^_^*\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/79551448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    上山啦~队伍拉的好长啊。。\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/34521448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/81411448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    看！藏龙洞里的龙！\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/82501448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/35861448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    本次寻宝第一处奖品被找到\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/28191448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    　　藏宝点共有三处，前两处各有两份宝贝，可上面这位大哥，愣是凭着敏锐的观察力拿到两个奖品，一份是密室逃脱的门票，一份是旅游护照，不能不说，大哥，您太牛了！\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    　　图片右边是第一个藏宝地两处藏宝点，大哥跟山洞里找到的宝贝。密室逃脱门票4张，原价120元/张，团购价60元/张。\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    　　大哥，带上我一起玩呗~\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/21531448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    没找到第一处宝贝，向着第二处进发吧\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/65671448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    姑娘找到第二处宝贝\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    　　看到图片右边那个画圈的地方了吗？兑奖券其实不大，贴在树枝上，如果不抬头，如果不回头，根本看不到的，可这姑娘在别人都低头翻找的时候，淡定的抬脚伸胳膊，就那么拿到了...\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    　　话说，本次随队的工作人员都没看到...好想要啊.....拿着旅游护照出门玩不用花钱，多好。\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    　　奖品是每人两本旅游护照...价值98元/本...分别藏在图片右侧那两个地方。\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/92961448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    藏到墙缝里也能被你发现！\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    　　第三处宝贝是都江宴的现金卡，价值275元，拿着卡直接就可以消费，吃饭或者到店前台买酒水饮料、烟酒糖茶，就跟银行卡似的...<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    　　下山回去就能拿着卡去吃饭了，好爽啊...\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/46671448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    休息过后准备捞鱼去喽~<img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/10521448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/76071448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    山上的景色不错\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/61071448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/70251448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/73281448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/39751448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/93661448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/61681448961516.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n    \n    \n    停车场，玩了一天，咱们回家喽~\n</p><p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">\n            <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload1//20151201/1448960483513454.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"/>\n</p><p>\n</p><p>\n            <br/>\n</p>','/uploads/2016/0331/72fb3c9f439cfae7c9820e65ef273ea5.jpg','1459238727','1464922200','80','','','','45','承德兴隆县',NULL,'19',NULL,NULL,'','1',NULL,'','8月8日车加车俱乐部来了场【九龙潭自驾一日游】','0','','','10','45','83');-- <xjx> --
