 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/29621452156995.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/2861452156995.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/30621452156995.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/63701452156995.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/16471452156995.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/64951452156995.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/73331452156995.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/43671452156995.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/88591452156995.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">        <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/55971452156995.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; text-align: center;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    经过两天的旅程，大家从陌生到朋友，从开始的放不开，到后来频频爆出笑声，虽有辛苦，但收获了真诚。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    　　感谢大家此次参加车加车网俱乐部的自驾游，感谢你们在此过程中对我们工作人员的支持和理解，更感谢你们在旅途中给予我们的快乐！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    \n    　　谢谢大家！希望下次我们依然同行！　　</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">        <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 感谢本次自驾游支持：星光大道，为我们提供价值800元的亲情卡、玻璃水、纸抽、优惠保养，再次感谢！</span></p><div>        <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></div><p>        <br/></p>','/uploads/2016/0331/30d5d207ace5ea64bf59b5e2e0b1d649.jpg','1459238876','1465346328','114','','','','49','张北',NULL,'19',NULL,NULL,'','1',NULL,'','9月12日，车加车网俱乐部跟大家一起去张北看了