/span></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 36px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 192, 163); border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\">先说交通</section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">石家庄距离秦皇岛大约570公里，路况较好，开车大概需要7个小时。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">好心献上我的自驾路线图：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">石家庄——京石高速——荣乌高速——京沪</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">高速——滨保高速——唐津高速——京哈高速——S251/出海路。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/b019fbf3059c1a720067902500915ab6.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">你说啥？不想开车？这都不是事儿！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">石家庄到秦皇岛每天有不少的高铁、动车及其它车次，高铁三个多小时就能到，普通列车需要7、8个</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">小时，二等高铁座位要240多块钱。不要心疼钱，出去玩就要玩得舒服些。</span></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"45\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; float: left; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 32px; vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(72, 192, 163);\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: table; width: 32px; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"autonum\" placeholder=\"1\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\">2</section></section></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 36px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 192, 163); border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\">关于住宿</section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">要是在旺季去秦皇岛北戴河的话，一定要在网上提前订好住的地方，不但能够省钱，还可以保证你玩得痛快。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">小编在此着重推荐一下北戴河刘庄家庭旅馆，它距离海</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">滨只有几百米，交通便捷，配套设施啥的也挺齐全的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/204025ea5dbe7a961df716638887ccb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">这整个村都是开家庭旅馆的，每家价格都差不太多，淡季50-60元，旺季在100-300元之间。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">我们定的是刘庄育花二区17排的半夏小栈（图中小红点的位置），因为喜欢这个名字，所以毫不犹豫选择了它，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">看来名字很重要。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/07c1369b90a8f4f831198442f5d968c4.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">当然，你想住好一点，也可以。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">北戴河有华茂喜来登酒店、观海楼、华北电力大厦等，市区里边还有香格里拉（总之是高档</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">次高消费，你能承受得起，就去住呗）。</span></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"45\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; float: left; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 32px; vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(72, 192, 163);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3</span></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 36px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 192, 163); border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\">再说餐饮</section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">根据以往经验总结出，北戴河景区没有好吃不宰人的饭店，至少我没有发现。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">因此想去北戴河吃海鲜的孩纸们可以放弃了，真想吃的话就在街边买两串烤鱿鱼解馋吧，或者去当地的海鲜市场买新鲜的回来自己加工。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/86b5c88b233a5030b9f02ea5cd8a2214.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">坑的就是外地人，所以一定要小心，可别再吃出个天价虾，你下辈子就扣那里给人家洗盘子抵债吧。</span></p></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"45\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; float: left; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 32px; vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(72, 192, 163);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4</span></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 36px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 192, 163); border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\">注意事项</section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">1.去海边一定要注意防晒哦，各种防晒霜、防晒喷雾、防晒衫、遮阳伞、遮阳帽啥的都用起来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">2.一定要带上美美的泳衣，旱鸭子们记得带上救命的泳圈（你若嫌麻烦，可以到了再买）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">3.海鲜不要随便吃、也不要多吃，不然拉肚子就惨了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">4.不要高估自己的泳技，每年都有死人的，所以不要太装逼，no zuo no die。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">5.总之，出门旅游不要太天真，太天真就容易受伤，自己要好好照顾自己嘞！！！</span></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"45\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; float: left; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 32px; vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(72, 192, 163);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5</span></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 36px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 192, 163); border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\">具体行程</section></section></section></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85741\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section class=\"layout\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86516\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); box-sizing: border-box;\"><h2 class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 0px 5px 6px; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); display: inline-block; line-height: 1.1;\">DAY 1</h2></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">早上六点从家出发，行李早已打包好塞进后备箱，只留下零食随身携带，一边吃一边打发路上的无聊时间。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">一路上心情好到爆，一路高歌，一路吃不停，我已然成了脱缰的野马！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/c4e1026c18cd9ad8d2162228df715d65.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">下午一点半到达刘庄，老板早已在路边等着我们，好nice的老板呢，还亲自指挥我们将车停在了便于进</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">出的地方。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">上一张旅店内部图，干净整洁，价格便宜，从窗户可以直接看见大海。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/56305a697ff633374d67768c48dcce73.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">安顿好行李，随便在路边吃了两个肉包子，撒丫子跑向海边了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">五六分钟的步行路程就可到达海边，住在刘庄的好处显而易见啊。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/c91592de1103e79dd4bc94acb0657f4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">由于是公共海滩，感觉海水不是特别的干净，有一点点发黑，但依然阻挡不了我下海游泳的热情。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/1dbd4a294a94553d3dd80490071b3514.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">谁让我是</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">内陆来的孩纸呢，单看见大海就很兴奋了，哪里还会挑剔那么多呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">中间那大哥，咋这么正经呢，你是来视察的么？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/45c1bb9affec4af841574867d27f8e1c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">撒完野，游完泳，晒完太阳，沿着海边一路向前走。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">快看我的大脚丫子~~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/694b1e53f34d227b89a76f72da17e17f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">这是谁建的小城堡呢？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/f52590f110e162f7896e3468c60a3486.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">沿途的北戴河海滨附近有很多政府和企业的疗养院，出门便是大海，住在这里心情想必是好极了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/62dadb384b2e6c1cc8061d832dcd4443.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">沿着海边一直走到北戴河海滨的中海滩，沿海的保二路商业街</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">是仿俄罗斯远东风格改建的，看起来很有异域风情。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/ae52c2e519f4dae45f89e23d5c9805cc.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/8d38e7197a3afeef80ceaac3f278fb49.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">老虎石公园就在这一带，不知为什么要收8块钱的门票。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">不过花得挺值的，比起公共海滩，这里的沙子细多</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">了，软软的，一点也不硌脚。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/89529d34c727546c8d04694a562ed613.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/0a95f2e5fded84003583505549cc11e3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">在老虎石公园门口被一卡通人偶拉过去照相，没想到是个骗局，拍一张要收10块钱的，以后可不敢随便乱拍</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">照了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">关键照的还不好看，所以就不上图了，大家自己小心吧，天上不会掉馅饼滴。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/8e4bb4128bd86ba5056eadec32e75218.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">犯懒，不想走回去了，直接打的到旅馆，两人10块钱，还好没有遇到黑心司机。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/9e7c493afdf52b951c61844d018d234f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">回到旅店，突然特别想吃海鲜，央求老板带我们去附近的海鲜市场买最新鲜的海鲜，这样就不会担心吃到天价海鲜了。我好聪明，有木有</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/5b3468fbdc4bc78efeee4323fdc481e5.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">老板好心帮我们加工，当然还是要给老板一点加工费的，不然谁白白给你做。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">一顿饭，两个大螃蟹，一大盆皮皮虾，一盘青菜，外加一盘海鲜炒饭，加上加工费，两个人一共才花了</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">150块钱，撑死我了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">老板娘的手艺还是不错哒，好吃~~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/199af4906c15900177262f3016e22bdc.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/3598a6550e1fee9fc00e06e6344dcb46.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/6db70cef3a08670398865a7d329d1750.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">吃饱饱，睡觉觉，期待第二天的鸽子窝日出。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86516\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); box-sizing: border-box;\"><h2 class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 0px 5px 6px; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); display: inline-block; line-height: 1.1;\">DAY 2</h2></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">怕耽误看日出，定的早上三点半的闹铃，迷迷糊糊穿衣洗漱，下楼。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">糟了，昨晚忘记告诉老板给开门了，这可咋办，还好大门上贴有电话，很不好意思地把老板叫醒了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">为了节省时间，我们直接开车到鸽子窝公园（门票25块钱一个人）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/55b788d8ef2329bb74ecce889b089dab.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">公园门口售票处，醒目地提示着游人每月每日观看日出的绝佳时间。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/dd5d311bc57264af64f9959ba139f2ed.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">虽然是夏季，海边还是有些冷滴，后悔没有穿外套出来啊，冻shi宝宝了，但这并没有影响我看</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">日出的心情。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">公园里安静极了，可以很清楚地听到海涛的声音，突然间幸福感爆棚。I am so lucky!!</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/ecbfc9c2e71cfd671914e78565bfbe8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/b54ff7b4da1cd672b40724426caa288c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">日出时分，万籁俱寂，色彩随之变幻，红日涌出的水面的刹那间，美爆啦！！！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">霞光洒满山峦、海面、沙滩。此刻，我好想呐喊咩……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/e6010a1ec12f24a5050c2561ad416e1f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">去海边的朋友们一定要去看日出哦，真的很漂亮，很神圣。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/c1e1790e0d318e3c0ca6f16f18561b19.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">看完日出，心情大好，抓小螃蟹咯。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">掀开大石头，下面好多这种东东，还有好多小螃蟹，太小了，拍的不是很清楚。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/c8564bf4cc3ea5c6e12c3868b4f6eea1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">我没有桶，但也有准备，饮料瓶，看到了吗？战果很丰富，有小鱼、小虾、还有小螃蟹，其</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">中螃蟹居多，大都是从石头底下翻出来的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/d1594022d5a15dbafeee163ad4a96974.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">好饿啊，大早上起来到现在都没有吃东西，还是先回宾馆吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">出来的时候正好拍到一群贪吃的鸽子。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/ef5c14f6e769e80693966f131c09f76b.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">家庭旅馆区到处都是卖早点的，随意走进一家早点店，点了鸡蛋油条咸菜，味道一般，价格公道</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/10d7ee02f3a3a0acc4b0db9cecf05639.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">回房间收拾行李，开车准备到下一个目的地——阿那亚三联书店海边公益图书馆，号称“世上最孤独的图书馆</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">”，是有多孤独呢？？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/c93cd635468f0430284721f11bc0437f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">我们大约九点从刘庄出发，不到十点半就到了图书馆所在的昌黎黄金海岸工业园区</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">这地方好啊，随手一拍就是摄影大片。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/2b4ef28224650a1c271e292c48880124.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图书馆位于一个叫“阿那亚”的高档海边社区里，住的都是高富帅，然而这并不是重点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">重点是你必须在官</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">方微信公众号“孤独图书馆”中预留身份证信息预约，他们每天只接待200名游客。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/003ee4ddab7633d843841ddd496ff928.JPG\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">重要的事情说三遍，要</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">预约！要预约！要预约！不预约就只能吃闭门羹了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">社区门口都是军人把守，不是递根儿烟，说两句好听的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">就能解决的事儿。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/ceae982c4a819841da61c17c3c907282.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">偶遇孤独的教堂，好想在这里举办一场属于自己的婚礼！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/20a29a3d0d521125ee42d69f56c590be.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">沿着海边一直向北溜达就到图书馆了，真的是超级孤独，周边没有任何建筑，也没什么人，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6;\">它就静静地伫立在海边。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/0e505afda148e456255816ec9b2d233a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/0ff1785b2250cbc6f11693df174411db.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">图书馆是个二层小楼，内部不大，白天利用屋顶上的洞洞采集光线。所以如果是阴天，里面还是挺昏暗的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/04ba0f6953afe94c19f43f8202aaa532.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/bcf71919ae43a672f0999eb0fbd844e1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">一进图书馆就被保安提醒，不允许在里面照相，然而并没有什么卵用。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/26ea112193c025e143301f9ef63e79d8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">逼格够高的吧，我承认我就是来拍照的，不是来看书的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/83c9516c1a122e02f43fa2716fe07c65.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">他们提供借阅的书籍谈不上多，但已经足够在这里消磨一天了。反正你也不是来看书的！！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/d3de3bc9ea2e632df911c2a652433f9e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">馆内设有一排沙发座，面对海滩，看够了书</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">可以看看外面的景色，国内绝无仅有的体验。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/d6c06d1b934e2dad6a5db3be084f21cb.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图书馆内部只有一个咖啡厅，一瓶Starbucks的咖啡45元，手调咖啡40元（如果没猜错，应该就是雀巢咖啡</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/de2321d105237c227fd0573e411d87a2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">好想就这样一直面朝大海，发呆，希望时间永远停留在这静谧的一刻啊。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/4deb160aeb7f7b2c20d4f9e175cbea12.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-botto