&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/ce3ff7a4524e74b132dc9441477c39e6.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">最近火起来的尔康表情包更是掀起一股还珠狂潮。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/e918e76eff416f8f53bc9ef5f8ade67a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">心中的小火苗被慢慢燃烧，好吧，那就去承德，皇帝的选择，哈哈哈。</span></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86516\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); box-sizing: border-box;\"><h2 class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 0px 5px 6px; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); display: inline-block; line-height: 1.1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 172, 213);\">第一天</span></h2></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">为早点赶到承德，七点就开车上路了，后备箱装满了各种零食、水和饮料，谁让咱是大胃王呢！迎着朝阳，一路向北，心中美美哒！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">时间比较早，所以路上不堵车，建议自驾游的同志们早些出发，避免堵在路上，车塞心也塞。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">出国际庄走新元高速公路，转京港澳高速公路，到京承高速，上大广高速，途经</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">N多个小村小庄。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">11点到北京高速服务区，补充能量，稍作休息，继续前进。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/0271003ea8ab8bfc3fc14a3f5ac5237f.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">下午两点半到达承德市区。因为所要游玩的景点比较集中，都在双桥区，所以提前预定了两晚新世纪热河大酒店的标间，185块钱一晚上，价格还算合适，紧邻城隍庙、避暑山庄等景点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">房间还不错，干净整洁卫生，还好提前预定，当天房间全部订空。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/909c61ea144f69871f37563913b45c3a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">三点收拾妥当，开玩咯！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">出酒店就是都统府大街，沿大街西行可到广仁大街，大约步行十分钟便到达“自封天下第一”的热河城隍庙，自己夸自己，真是毫不谦虚啊。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">庙不</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">大，我们就随意乱逛起来了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">哦，对了，门票两个人一共花了40块钱，挺便宜的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/f3a3dfc9611f52f22a110f001e322098.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">庙里的工作人员说每天上午九点到十点有道教法事活动，可惜没赶上。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">好想看道士们是如何施法的，小妖哪里逃，收！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">菩萨一定要保佑发大财啊，南无阿弥佗佛！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">等我发大财了，一定回来还愿！给多多的香火钱！！</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/4e69f80e4e095cad02d7fcb86f9297a6.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">无意中发现庙宇深处一个不知名小建筑物，感觉写满了历史故事。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/c206d97694ec54ce176469142d6e4914.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">逛了没多一会就逛完了，出庙吃饭。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">由于在市区，吃饭不成问题，各种高低中档餐馆都有。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">离城隍庙不远，就在返回酒店的路上，有一家老三羊汤馆，口碑不错。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">瞧“老三羊汤”这四个大字，大老远就瞅见了。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/e7d3dc2bab10d38d4c8acfbc5d05cd35.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">我们两只喜欢喝羊汤的小盆友，40块钱搞定承德的第一餐。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/c834117088635a1fb6110c8438ae1f9e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">今天的行程到此结束，回窝睡觉。晚上梦到我成为新一代女皇！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/82aa763638aee1e7583ac2ae1d5f07b3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86516\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); box-sizing: border-box;\"><h2 class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 0px 5px 6px; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); display: inline-block; line-height: 1.1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 172, 213);\">第二天</span></h2></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">第二天当之无愧要献给避暑山庄咯，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">怕在景区饿肚子，背了一背包的干粮。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">主要还是钱紧，山庄里吃饭太贵怎么办？卖了小伙伴换钱？嘿嘿~~细想想主意还是不错的~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">离得近，仍旧选择步行，一路向北便可到达售票处——丽正门（</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">门票145大洋）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/64ea5097380e644935b610fde56c9de2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">先上一张游览图，太复杂，不然说不明白。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">山庄分为湖区、平原区以及山区三部分，右下方为湖区，右上方为平原区，左上方为山区。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/1f62b883cf5b79e376e9c1cf45e9157c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">在这个混吃混喝的社会，“蹭”字大行其道，蹭导游，别不好意思，不蹭白不蹭。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">导游肚子里全是野史、传说，非常有意思，我们蹭的美女导游讲起话来全是笑点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">偷拍的美女导游，中间穿裙子的红衣女子，身材很是让人羡慕呀。</span></span><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/253b1f3d2c83223cb272b26d1596ee82.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">湖区多亭台、水榭、楼阁，半数以上都是由康熙、乾隆爷孙俩命名的，这一大家子简直太有柴了，赞一个。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/42beb9ae26f49a061b54be5985a84f80.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px;\">本想着为每一个景点、每一个亭楼阁宇都拍照留念呢，无奈太多了，还是挑我喜欢的和大家分享吧。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px;\">进门不远处的</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">小金</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">銮殿，全是用楠木搭建的，偷偷用指甲抠了一下，很硬的，怪不得千年不朽呢。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/b3a0e4aa0bf0822f7ff0c6c6060a71ee.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">右行穿过小桥便是文园狮子林，顾名思义，以假山石林为主咯。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/150670984b4104c21c86e63f0d1cab7b.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">据说，假山嶙峋这一景点是由鼎鼎有名的和大人设计的，和大人也蛮有艺术细胞的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/3e82dbafb48f0f079b87224fcac098ad.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">前行是冷香亭，在亭子里可看到对面的游船中心。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/b17548134162d066ad6e9ff70faec486.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">穿过连接冷香亭的石桥，到达如意湖西岸的上船点。想荡舟湖面，于是我们两个人花40块钱租了一小时的脚踏船，好像回到了童年！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">在船上拍到的对岸楼阁，漂亮死了。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/ef77aeab540cc436a5a8d7f26a50af7b.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">下船沿弯弯的湖边向北，终于看到了烟雨楼。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">漱芳斋的取景地就是这里，我小时候的偶像小燕子格格的闺房。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/75fdacb94c60042d3f9bcf00d2f64ca4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">烟雨楼的正脸，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px;\">帝皇乎？神仙乎？这景漂亮得也是没sei了。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/e1fce63b43180d32c598a106d5e78543.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">再往前行就能看到万树园了，以前皇上狩猎的地方。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">如果搁现在，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">乾隆</span>说不定就建个万树园高尔夫球场什么的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/5e112fcd0285d653d1f73aad934b32aa.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">路遇热心的本地大妈，推荐山庄石泉，天然的山泉水，现打现喝，绝对凉快。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">少喝点，拉肚子我可不管，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">瓶里是刚接的山泉水。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/71cf2b0d379ba99f74834408bd9b9cc8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">看过湖区和山区，吃了一点自带的干粮，喝了一点山泉水，便来到环山车的地方。山区太大了，我们只有一天的时间，不可能步行走完山区。花40块钱坐车围着山区转了一圈，大约一个小时。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">要说这些皇帝们可真会消遣，竟将整个的苍茫山岭圈进来供自己娱乐。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">由于坐车不方便拍照，所以拍的照片很少，大家凑合看一下吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/7ed7bd2efc77e1dd10d6cfa247e3e0f3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/db2227ec6c6affedd14d53985ceabf4e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">出山门，回酒店，太累了，随便在路边吃了一点东西，赶紧回去养精蓄锐，明天还有任务呢。</span></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86516\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); box-sizing: border-box;\"><h2 class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 0px 5px 6px; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); display: inline-block; line-height: 1.1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 172, 213);\">第三天</span></h2></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">旅行最后一天，一大早起来收拾行李、退房，直接开车去最具“颜值”的普陀宗乘之庙，咱河北的布达拉宫，40块钱一个人，比去西藏便宜多了。</span></span></p></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">盗一张全景图震撼一下各位看官，我没航拍机器，不然肯定拍的更漂亮！！</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/4bfe3ae08d9e03aa602d6d920a8f49e4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 1.6;\">进山门，沿着中轴线向前，主要景点都在中轴线两侧。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">距离入口不远处就是五塔门，是不是很像布达拉。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">墙上的窗户称为“盲窗”，据说是为了不让小喇嘛看到外面的花红柳绿和人间凡俗，才这样做的，小可怜儿们。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/82f8b273ac9112f31518020234820876.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">由于今天要返程，不敢耽搁太多时间在庙里，琉璃牌坊、东罡殿、西罡殿、白台等景点都简单掠过，直接上大红台，到万法归一殿。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/aefc3d2d53a23b9dec984e86a258662e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">这么高的台阶，爬上去累虚脱了，小萝莉真是太有活力了，一直蹦蹦跳跳走在我们前边。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/31059d435b545b203758adea5525df79.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">万法归一殿的金顶，据说是用一万五千两黄金做成的，有钱，任性！</span><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/32e4a6850be9a1e50aeb865193dcab13.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">看完万法归一殿，从东掖门出，出口入口是分开的，还得绕一圈回到停车场取车。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">无意中经过一家大清花，那午餐就是它了。大清花的饺子果然名不虚传，石家庄也有分店哦，具体位置大家自己问度娘。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/56c226e52187377a03acd548c7689bd5.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">薄皮大馅，绿绿的韭菜、白白的虾仁、黄黄的鸡蛋，那叫一个鲜呐！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0623/fe0994dd476c3c8e7c5055341c0f9e66.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">喂，口水流下来了，快擦擦！说的就是你！</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">很遗憾，这次来承德竟然没有骑马，只能相约下次再策马奔腾咯！</span></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"29735\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; width: 92px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; color: inherit; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); color: rgb(255, 129, 36);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); color: inherit;\">TIPS：</strong></span></p></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section data-width=\"50%\" style=\"margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; line-height: 10px; height: 8px; width: 269px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);\"></section></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-style=\"text-indent: 2em;\" style=\"margin: 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: inherit; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 22.4px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 25px;\">景区票价：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 25px;\">城隍庙20元，避暑山庄145元，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px;\">普陀宗乘之庙40元（不包含景区内其它娱乐费用）。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">全程距离：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">约520公里。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">自驾线路：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">石家庄—新元高速—京港澳高速—京承高速—大广高速—承德。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 22.4px;\">温馨提示：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); line-height: 22.4px;\">出发前，要备好一些必要物资哦！比如说拉肚子、感冒、蚊虫叮咬的药物！还有，承德天气凉，记得拿几件春秋衣衣！记得保护好随着携带的钱财物品，牵好你的同伴！拿好电话，随时保持联系！地方太大，丢了实在不好找。。</span></p></section><section data-width=\"65%\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; line-height: 10px; text-align: right; height: 10px; width: 349.688px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px auto 1px; padding: 0px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(255, 129, 36); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);\"></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\">​<img src=\"/uploads/2016/0627/b3911b53e724118a6281ad29e2b0726e.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br/></p></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','/uploads/2016/0623/11f58855dd7bfd03140fd9e4f93a51f9.jpg','1466667654','1467008728','46','','承德','','51','承德',NULL,'16',NULL,NULL,'','0',NULL,'','...','0','','','10','51','85');-- <xjx> --
