('45','0','43','河北的亲们，夏日专项福利终于来了！','','','','飒飒','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9kqW5VBFK8jKWBlsDjaUX0NXX8kbs9M36VrmXkYky4sKiapqeWqIKkb5DWLy6nA5ib4HvbBzUNHbS5w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.11690647482014388\" data-w=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">最近庄里的气温直线上升，已经把我热到膨胀、热成包拯、热到扭曲、热到旋转、热到与太阳肩并肩、热到我要人间蒸发啊。不管了，本姑娘要寻一个深山老林给自己降温去了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9nJx5uSRROSFZHE3eDheMXDUwKHgc54hofEVn61w1PNBlqEuc725Gp59UH9202u4hHarDEN01e0Xg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.582\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">去哪里呢？下班时候突然</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">在十字路口LED大显示屏上看到京娘湖的广告了，说得贼好，什么玻璃栈道，丛林漂流、高空滑锁balabala的，看着就凉快。既然你被我看到了，那我就选择你吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"></span></p><p></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><p class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86695\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;\"><img data-ratio=\"0.046341463414634146\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibHB1zic0rPepxuU7vOmqPUicgAicNTHfnQVExVoaTYegdKibqia6b1EpcjibibrKMvAcDpTfVHxEooepkBhQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-w=\"410\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;\"/></p><p class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86695\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86695\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">关于交通</strong></span></p></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">去之前，先搜了一下路线。石家庄市区到京娘湖单程3.5个小时车程。大约2.5个小时高速、1小时盘山路（此处重点强调，请接着往下看！我会重点说明）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyYE2LDyKwQCIW2tBypoFSXD1y5N5vw6F45eictQKmXGborpNty8loeRw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-w=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">从高速出来后，就要进入盘山路了，这个盘山路开了接近50分钟，为什么？全是弯！！！再次提醒：全是弯！！！并且都是180度这种大折线！大家进入盘山路时，一定要小心、小心、再小心。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">在盘山路上看到两起车祸。一起是俩车迎头相撞，貌似应该是因为乱串车道引起的；另一起是一个奥迪A6剐蹭了一个当地村里的小摩托。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">再次友情提示：致富千日功，车祸一日穷！小心使得万年船！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"></span></p><p></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><p class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86695\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;\"><img data-ratio=\"0.046341463414634146\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibHB1zic0rPepxuU7vOmqPUicgAicNTHfnQVExVoaTYegdKibqia6b1EpcjibibrKMvAcDpTfVHxEooepkBhQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-w=\"410\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); line-height: 25.6px;\">关于住宿</strong></span></p></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">之前也有过不少的旅行，每一次都计划满满的，来也匆匆，去也匆匆。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">这次决定放慢脚步，周六下午出发，晚上在景区住一宿，第二天再去游玩。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">提前一天在网上定的松林山庄，三星级的宾馆，哈哈哈，当地比较好的宾馆，紧挨着景区。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyXoot61y4VtTdiaiaW56iciaYCwpCQqCRQKlmCJ2fHxtlytORL1ZAicuics2w/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-ratio=\"0.674\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">一共五个人，三男两女，一个三人间（159块），一个标间（168块），足矣，比现场订房要稍微便宜一些。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><p class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86695\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;\"><img data-ratio=\"0.046341463414634146\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibHB1zic0rPepxuU7vOmqPUicgAicNTHfnQVExVoaTYegdKibqia6b1EpcjibibrKMvAcDpTfVHxEooepkBhQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-w=\"410\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\">关于门票</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">提前一天在某网上买的门票，包含船票，一个人85块，不包含景区内其它的娱乐设施。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">建议各位，一定要乘船游览，不然你会后悔一辈子的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">景区内的各项设施还是不少的，观光车单程10块，小火车10块，缆车单程40块，滑锁40块，这些我没有在网上查到优惠票。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">此外，还有新开放的丛林漂流，原价50块，不定期有活动，可惜没有玩；</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">玻璃栈道的活动没有赶上，30块钱一个人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">去之前，各位同胞可先广泛搜集一下信息，看有没有优惠购票，能省下来不少钱。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><p class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86695\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; border: 0px none;\"><img data-ratio=\"0.046341463414634146\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/yqVAqoZvDibHB1zic0rPepxuU7vOmqPUicgAicNTHfnQVExVoaTYegdKibqia6b1EpcjibibrKMvAcDpTfVHxEooepkBhQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-w=\"410\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; display: inline;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">具体行程</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\"></span></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"45\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; float: left; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 32px; vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(72, 192, 163);\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: table; width: 32px; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"autonum\" placeholder=\"1\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\">1</section></section></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 36px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 192, 163); border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\">第一天</section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">周六下午一点半左右，老周家门口集合，一行五人浩浩荡荡地向山沟沟进发了，经过三个半多小时的颠簸，经过九曲十八弯的磨难，下午五点一刻到达景区。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhy5YibyibqsM9MMsYLgD9hcytSibFQ1g62PZlQ0FvstQ5gCdBzmuue3VgWQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">接近景区，一眼就看见我们的宾馆了，在一群住宿之中鹤立鸡群，可以算是景区比较好的宾馆了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">出来玩么，不在乎这百八十块的，玩得开心、住得舒心最重要了。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">宾馆外面的图片照虚了，大家凑活看吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9nJx5uSRROSFZHE3eDheMXDB8TWRF0dKXKfDRfuwRNWabCdZ9mZLQSjQccE1m511nxJddWNqQqafQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.562363238512035\" data-w=\"457\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">上楼，我们两位女汉子的房间真不错，从窗户可以直接看到湖景，美了美了，醉了醉了~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyHOBs7TOKlrFv8PNAvfhUNIY3TmFsTaia97MA8kTm3cZelefEX25mdxg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8299595141700404\" data-w=\"494\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">收拾好东西，下楼溜达溜达，一出宾馆门看到一家小饭店，名字不太记得了，光顾着拍菜，然后吃吃吃了。五个人点了五个菜，一盘烧饼，三碗米饭，两瓶饮料，一共花了328块钱。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">景区内有不少小吃店，随便选吧，价格差不了多少。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">上几道有特色的邯郸名吃，酥鱼、烧鸡、驴肉肠、烧饼，味道不错。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyHETc6Cta3V94kkTkYVA8df58IlGCkIZSB6vBwDmu30B6cfgvHjRCIQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.3709090909090909\" data-w=\"550\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">吃完，溜达溜达，消消食。风从水库上吹过来，温度比市里边低了好几度，凉快。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">回到宾馆，完全没有睡意，从宾馆前台要了扑克牌，轮流打起来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">瞧这姐妹的洗牌姿势，专业!</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9la0ib0TUNUvQB7t7u97Ak6Bb0HwcLJgFiaZpoYQiatxRic3R7PWR3ZDbuKTv6NE8T4VoPpo3TicHibe8Hw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>我说张哥啊，你是猴子派来的逗逼么？就你身上这点料还好意思往外抖？！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9la0ib0TUNUvQB7t7u97Ak6BsGodlKZ6I1TA0kCicsePIo2NLPpAUBstKytc1cP9n2BBQAKkCjOjN7w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.1782178217821782\" data-w=\"404\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>一帮人闹腾到半夜12点多才散了，不能再玩了，不然第二天没力气爬山了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">山里的夜晚真安静，还能看见好多星星，浪漫……<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>晚上跟二丫躺在床上，聊着聊着天就睡着了，zzz……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"></span></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"45\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; float: left; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 32px; vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(72, 192, 163);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2</span></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 36px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 192, 163); border-color: rgb(72, 192, 163); box-sizing: border-box;\">第二天</section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">一大早被走廊里嚷嚷的声音吵醒了，睁眼一看才过7点，还想着多睡会呢。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">从门缝里偷偷看过去，原来是一波刚到的客人在办理入住。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">素质、素质，麻烦小点声音，宝宝还想再睡会呢!</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">那就起来洗漱洗漱，准备出发吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">洗漱的时候，老周过来敲门，问我们要不要吃早餐，没睡醒，不想去，直接面包牛奶凑活一下吧。</span></p><p style=\"mar