车就差不多到山顶了，俗话说，不来宋祖峰枉来京娘湖，我这登上山顶了，没遗憾了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyHnRqAMQI3LA5nJUVZicAOLhmFuTD1QouwxI57SgibaucjRN9qsa06OBA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.33\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">宋祖峰的云中寺，石栏的两边都挂满了祈福的红布条。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyviclHqzw3NNI2icN4iaqmZ022XaaBibibu4SXHBDPyX6aVNnTQmy2E3dtibQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.33\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>寺里的大钟，好像敲钟是要收钱的，收多少不太清楚，因为不感兴趣，也就没有问。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhy27r8lwQ7MqCrA0JmkVD4JYLjXSuq6bjzthx8b7cUspGAbFthUb0E2g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">接下来，就是我最期待的玻璃栈道了<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0p