gin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">都不贵，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">炒面、拽面都是10元钱一碗，凉粉5元一碗。这可是在景区内啊。同志们！敢问哪个地方的4A级景区有这等便宜的物价！赞一个！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">吃饱了、喝足了，下山也有劲了，下山途中的京娘雕像。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyIeCFRZia7y2Kuke5SLAIqR2eJywdwspkgjtExic9TBAa8ExZzVKy6Dfg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.33\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>雕像下边石碑上刻的颂京娘。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyuL7y11LmuJu6RczqzoIlicIclaicCP6gcHiacuIzPCnFS02yM1tGzgXfA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.33\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>京娘雕像旁边的京娘祠</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyHU3jo803Jic1ehggtiad7cXGQiaFmKcNoFQTApzibdpVCdqQ3bDZCgicBQw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">里边还有京娘的蜡像呢，京娘果真是个大美人，怪不得赵匡胤要千里送京娘！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyCtpSKHVc7jicWHejasfYEJJgRLZibc0wTxoTpdYh4c1u8yxHBN4n588A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.168\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">从京娘祠出来，有三条路，一是走栈道到鹊桥，结束游览；二是走老虎洞到鹊桥结束游览；三是直接滑索出溜回去。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">选择恐惧症，好纠结，哪个都想走一遍啊。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">旁边一小姑娘一直忽悠我们坐滑索，说多么好，越劝越不坐，就这么倔强，哈哈哈。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">虽然之前一直想走栈道，但小伙伴们觉得没有太大意思，想走一下更具挑战性的老虎洞。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">好吧，少数服从多数，那就老虎洞吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyxHTGVrtLiar0uaCUyMIhAFYduK8yiaaWj4jX3k7lLnTfSXCUYM8sxibQQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.642\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">果真是不试不知道，一试吓一跳，路超难走的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhy0eNtichxOohH8XadvfSiaJ8f8a1ibnIibPbH43JVHzFTzJ7b5qicCRrR7tA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">你看这坡陡的，至少得有70度吧。手一直紧紧抓着铁链子，我的小命就拴在这链子上了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhycoyRrsD98Tfzl5R8kgwFfk6cPgF1prsyj5902tatibvpcIKA0qDNZ2A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">继续往前，到达天缝，这叫一个窄呦，得亏我长得瘦。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">胖子由于体型太大，穿过去的时候费老鼻子劲了，逗死我们了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhySpfWI41HCFZ63k6EQ2MRmegl2xGRjIY3FPAiaLtPUohEKibKm5gRhF9Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">出了天缝，可看见湖面上的游船，这种感觉很奇妙。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyCgpH6jYISeyyOy6rGKGhGDc7oGfMrhHXVxhpiaux44tic6tdd3mdj0Lg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">要过鹊桥了，桥挺不错，站在上边视野很开阔。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">感觉自己瞬间成了七仙女，要和董永来相会。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhy5icLD0akqqUGP0JzbTyOnEk1piaxj1ibuiaDHlPEzctSollf2LURQevjGw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">在鹊桥拍到的悬崖上的栈道。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyLia2BOfN9Jjn3ZBCrWprAu2q9k7kbh3AUCPeCAvcA7JNK7ibJgXjiauhg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">在鹊桥上可看到滑索，恰巧有一个人滑过，抓拍了一张，不是很清楚。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mDEVK2Gu3eBO7ibia9AO6lhyt0duU2d1mX5xwnrG4Wr4jx7ymamfLiaM3K2iaqEicEaqc0qmRCmaCmpAA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.476\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">下鹊桥，京娘湖算是游览完了，一看时间已经接近下午两点钟，决定回酒店收拾东西、退房，直接往回返。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">又要回到庄里享受太阳的无限恩宠了！想到这儿，宝宝又不开森了！</span></p></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"3126\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: none rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; width: 40px; height: 40px; float: right; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 1px; box-shadow: rgb(103, 103, 103) -1px 1px 2px; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 20px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(153, 153, 153) rgb(153, 153, 153); box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"margin: -38px 0px 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border-width: 18px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(255, 255, 255) rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;\"></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;\"><section data-width=\"80%\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; width: 438.391px; height: 40px; line-height: 1.5em; border-bottom-width: 5px; border-bottom-style: solid; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(239, 112, 96); border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;\">温馨小提示：</span></strong></section></section><section class=\"135brush\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 8px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(239, 112, 96); box-sizing: border-box; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">全程：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">大约220公里</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">时间：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">大约3.5h</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">自驾路线：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">石家庄——青银高速——京港澳高速——邢衡高速——邢汾高速</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">乘车路线：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">火车/汽车到邯郸，在<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; line-height: 1.6;\">邯郸市西客站进站口乘坐公交808旅游专线可直接到京娘湖，周六周日早八点各一班，下午五点的回程。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">*开车有危险，行车需谨慎</span></strong></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></p></section></section><p></p><p><br/></p>',NULL,'1467265957','1467265957','0','','','',NULL,'',NULL,'15,16',NULL,NULL,'','1',NULL,'','...','0','','','10','0','83');-- <xjx> --
INSERT INTO `sline_article` VALUES
('46','0','44','“日进斗金，四季皆秋”之地就在你身边，你知道么？','','','','飒飒','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/ef5ccf6eda75a268de107a599b34ed35.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">从来都是眼睁睁地看着别人，就走就走，各种羡慕~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">而今，我也要经历一番说走就走的旅行。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">去哪里呢？哪里呢？哪里呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/89d506ba09476a9c384fe45ad624f681.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">掐指一算，荷花开得正好，那就去白洋淀吧，享有</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">”日进斗金、四季皆秋“之美誉的神奇之地。</span></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86514\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 538px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); text-align: center; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(61, 167, 66);\">交通方面</span></section><section data-bcless=\"lighten\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit; width: 538px; font-weight: bolder; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(172, 196, 136); border-bottom-style: dashed; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;\"></section><section style=\"margin: -20px 0px 0.5em 30px; padding: 0px; width: 25px; color: rgb(128, 177, 53); overflow: hidden; height: 28px; line-height: 26px; border: 2.6px solid rgb(128, 177, 53); border-radius: 20%; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">1</section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">石家庄到白洋淀大概有200公里的路程，开车需要3个小时。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">本人的自驾游路线：京港澳高速转荣乌高速，安新白洋淀口下（容城），下道右转直行。（进入安新县后，路交叉口设有白洋淀景区的指示路标）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/c9bc36ea831e649cd4a8d4ec1b6b648e.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">路况较好，路线十分简单，好走，好找。你只要祈祷别遇到堵车就可以了。</span></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86514\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 550px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); text-align: center; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(61, 167, 66);\">费用方面</span></section><section data-bcless=\"lighten\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit; width: 550px; font-weight: bolder; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(172, 196, 136); border-bottom-style: dashed; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;\"></section><section style=\"margin: -20px 0px 0.5em 30px; padding: 0px; width: 25px; color: rgb(128, 177, 53); overflow: hidden; height: 28px; line-height: 26px; border: 2.6px solid rgb(128, 177, 53); border-radius: 20%; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span class=\"autonum\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit;\">2</span></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">白洋淀旅游是自助游的形式，花什么钱享受什么样的服务。花钱的地方主要涉及到以下几点：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">1、停车费，一般是当天10块，过夜的话要20。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">2、入淀费，一人40块，当天有效。这钱收的有点毫无来由，交了入淀费进去玩还得买门票，什么鬼，占山为王。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">3、船费，自然是必不可少的，白洋淀到处都是水，不做船游玩怎可，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">码头不一样，船的价格也就不一样。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">枣林庄码头最贵，11人座快艇360元/条，离景点也最远；安新码头最大，价格次之，11人座快艇260元/条；雄县温泉城码头最小，价格中等，11人座快艇220元/条。距离景点最近的是“郭里口民俗村码头”，船费也最便宜，11人座快艇180元/条，离荷花大观园才2华里的水路。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">4、住宿费。白洋淀旅游住宿主要有这么几种：最经济实惠是100元/人，包吃住；临水双人标间100元/间，三人标准间120元/间，吃饭点餐；水上三星</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">木屋周末200元/间，非周末160元/间，吃饭点餐。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">5、餐费。餐费在旅游中占据很大的比重。一般情况下，自备酒水、饮料和零食，可以省不少钱。由于我们住的地方包吃饭，所以饭钱省下了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">6、景点门票。白洋淀是5A景区，主要的景点有9个，其中荷花大观园和白洋淀文化苑门票是50元/人，1.2米以下的孩子免票；其它像异国风情园、嘎</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">子印象、宝岛水上游乐园、鸳鸯岛、休闲岛等票价都是40元/人。</span></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86514\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; text-align: left;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 550px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); text-align: center; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(61, 167, 66);\">行程安排</span></section><section data-bcless=\"lighten\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: inherit; width: 550px; font-weight: bolder; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(172, 196, 136); border-bottom-style: dashed; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;\"></section><section style=\"margin: -20px 0px 0.5em 30px; padding: 0px; width: 25px; color: rgb(128, 177, 53); overflow: hidden; height: 28px; line-height: 26px; border: 2.6px solid rgb(128, 177, 53); border-radius: 20%; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; background: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span class=\"autonum\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit;\">2</span></section></section></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"39\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" placeholder=\"请输入标题\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; height: 36px; display: inline-block; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold; line-height: 36px; float: left; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">DAY1——荷花大观园</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; height: 36px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 9px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box; border-top-width: 18px !important; border-top-style: solid !important; border-top-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-width: 18px !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">我住西二环、K住东二环，一大早电话叫醒K，让他赶紧收拾东西过来接我。大约八点的时候K到小区门口，正式出发。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">因为K在安新县有项目，所以去过不少次，路是很熟悉的了，不用开导航，闭着眼睛就能找到路（好像说的有点夸张哈）。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">自打上车起，就一直祈祷不要堵车不要堵车，但还是在市里堵了，可能是周六，大家都出去玩吧，光从市里到高速路口这一段路就走了差不多一个半小时。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">我的心也是被堵得塞塞的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/eaa735524004a4751bcbd513b680949a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">终于上到了高速，还好高速上畅通无阻，既没有堵车，也没有发生交通事故，一路狂奔到安新白洋淀口。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">下高速后都十一点半了，赶紧给陈老板打电话，告诉他我们预计到达的时间，好过来接我们。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"></span></span></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"24\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section class=\"135brush layout\" style=\"margin: 3px auto; padding: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 3px; border: 2px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(255, 76, 0);\">说到这个陈老板，我插播一下：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">之前在网上做攻略，好多网友建议住王家寨民俗村，离景点都比较近，也比较有特色。然后又看到好多旅友们推荐王家寨2号院，基本上都一致好评，什么干净卫生啊、饭菜可口啊、老板人好之类的，还有热心网友提供老板电话。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">反正也不知道住哪里，就先打电话过去问问咯，电话打了好久才接通，因为老是有人占线，看来这个陈老板生意还不错。还好我们打得及时，老板那里还有两间房间可住，说是再晚点就没有了。于是赶紧定了一个标间，100块钱一个人，包吃住，挺划算的。老板告诉我们，快到的时候给他打电话，他过来接我们。</span></p></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">下高速之后 ，严格按照陈老板发来的路线走，路况很好，到赵庄子村码头下车（下图左下角红圈处），早有人在码头等我们了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">停好车，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">弃车登船！！！</span></p></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/fc8c72542810b33931e0c33fd0a053ad.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">白洋淀我来了，你准备好了吗？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">坐船大约10分钟就到了我们住宿的地方。接船一般是7人以下20元，超过的话30元。整个行程，由农家院安排，省去了自己联系这档子麻烦事。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/d0e57a611b8ce6e2d56a62c20de60230.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">下船码头，环境挺不错的，视野很开阔</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/c68d5103fab340942f474e15fe836b2a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">到了住宿的地方都快中午12点了，一进大门口就闻到了饭菜香味，原来老板娘刚做好饭，正在招呼大家吃饭。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/bc3874ad746a475ed2d6fbf28a46fe2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">老板娘问我们介意不介意跟同来的几个人一起吃，看到其中一小哥长得蛮帅的，赶紧说不介意不介意，人多热闹嘛。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/812e7879a16a32aeda68b118affe614f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">满满一桌子的菜，荤素都有，当然少不了当地著名的咸鸭蛋、松花蛋，腌的恰到好处，满满的都是金黄色的油，但是又不咸。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/0d4d21c09ad918c4543d5ccfb430396f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">吃完饭，一点多，舍不得休息，直接</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">出发去荷花大观园。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">我们就是坐着下面图片中间的这种小船，陈老板给安排的，100元/条，一个来回。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/0366600a305f1869a8d22083886a15a9.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">出行的话，5个人是最合适的。因为这样可以平摊船费（我们2个人，加上另外3个陌生人，正好是5个人）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">之前在网上查的入淀费是40元/人，实际上我们5个人，只交了一份，所以，每个人是8元的入淀费。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">一路上看到好多游船，都是去荷花大观园的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/d0cca5de8f5ea84401f25d641360b7f4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">接我们的船老大直接把我们送到大观园的南门，并约定还在南门接我们返回。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">大观园主要是以观赏荷花为主，喜爱拍照的朋友可以尽情发挥。园中面积不小，可以选择步行或者搭乘游览车。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/0d4c8c8ddeecaa50a21b82dc445b551b.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">对于我来说，步行参观大观园完全没问题。景区的电瓶车30一位，没必要乘坐。但是天气太热了，一定要带足水。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">从南门进，一眼看见的当然就是那个莲花观音塑像了，和观音娘娘神似，怎么看怎么别扭。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/3d5b14ff837c3411b97cad5504b7044b.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">向右手边方向走，到了精品荷花园，既有荷花区，也有睡莲区。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">精品荷花园有上百种荷花，很多是引进的舶来品。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/27395ffc8b38fb604781053fbea35b80.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">各种颜色，各种品种，各种名贵，各种禁止采摘~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/e06b367e68209c648917f22fa0b7d8ef.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/9e3778185bab39fbf1ed82cee1509465.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">每一张的荷花的品种都是不一样的，具体叫什么名字我也不知道。呵呵，总之一句话，都好看。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/9a3afb7ad734a17f2163da94464de25a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/a6d90f89220ccd6b5be19bc7999bbb4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">再往北走是观鱼湖，这鱼真够肥的。就知道吃，一直在抢食。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/b5c7d2dc2c94c54094ce812d40c051a7.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">走过观鱼湖，往西走，可以看到天鹅湖，成群的天鹅在水里游来游去。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/c7af29df5f4f19a48d0a07de287faf24.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">我觉得还是黑天鹅最好看，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">好像知道我要给它拍照一样，每一个动作都那么美。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/abe9ae81ecbae75bcff0d90dc88dd834.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/2bd1ebf51d9665bfd3d47f43344a6d11.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">偷偷拍摄的鱼鹰，哈哈，还好没有被大爷发现。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/8943b8b638f8758640cc37184ca55030.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">再往前，到了北门旁边的购物街，玲琅满目的商品，有草帽，草席，还有用蒲苇编制的蒲苇垫子等等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/475848545e846eddc51b081cb5e27ac6.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">过了北门，可到孙犁纪念馆，孙犁可是“荷花淀派”的创始人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/ed9ab050463837c9ae40e11271346e8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">​出孙犁纪念馆，看到水上有各种拓展项目，我最喜欢了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">各种娱乐设施，大人、小孩子都可以玩的~~~~~小心落水哦~~~~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">还好我技术过硬，没有落水。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/0879b8488216db89eefa5765747f7306.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">大概玩到了快六点，赶紧到南门，给船工师傅打电话。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">师傅说早就在门口等我们了，真是不好意思呢。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">从大观园归来，饭菜已经准备好了。回屋简单冲个凉，开始吃饭。旁边一桌刚钓鱼归来，收获不少，看那自带的垂钓装备就知道是高手。他们还相约晚上去夜钓，没有游船干扰肯定收获更丰。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/b660bb03283163af38dba224824380c2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">吃过晚饭在屋里躺着休息，好像是8点左右的时候</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">听到外面有放烟花的，很热闹，禁不住好奇心的趋势，出去看看去。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/f1809243d32e165e7e823d9180e2fcf8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">还有放孔明灯的。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/be323d4a04842621cbfce574da372a69.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">这一天就这样结束了</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"39\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" placeholder=\"请输入标题\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; height: 36px; display: inline-block; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold; line-height: 36px; float: left; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">DAY2——游野淀</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; height: 36px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 9px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box; border-top-width: 18px !important; border-top-style: solid !important; border-top-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-width: 18px !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">游野淀，只需要再掏100块钱的船费就可以了，是一条船100，不是一个人100！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">这是最经济实惠，又最有趣的路线了。因为，不需要重复交入淀费了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">但是：一定要早起去游玩。因为，早上空气好，而且游人特别少。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/fda096fbf5e5bcc9b967dd18a07dc6ad.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">我们早上5点多就起床洗漱，计划游玩回来再吃早饭。昨天晚上老板帮我们联系好船工，今儿一大早就过来接我们了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/2b04368496dde65e9a7dded2f6e499b2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">早晨的空气特别清新，视野也特别开阔，心情自然很开朗！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">清晨的野淀，除了我们，很少看到别人（除了驻扎在那里养大闸蟹的当地人）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/480fb39ea5f423f3191b7695edeed6e0.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">向着野淀出发！！！一路划船，很是惬意！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/eb3e2e75cdf5b75906e670025697d9a8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">两边芦苇荡里都是小野鸭，可惜，我们抓不到它……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">看，前面一只小野鸭在向我们秀它的水上滑翔技术呢！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/bc49e9f04041f60958e4dc0a0763abaa.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">在野淀，你也可以选择学习撑船哦！一边划船一边</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">采莲蓬，新鲜的莲蓬就是好吃，又脆又嫩又甜，中间的苦心都不用去！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/2c531992627cd0fc92ceef9d773ae86b.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">我想着带点新鲜的莲蓬回去给朋友尝尝，船工师傅二话不说，帮</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">我们采摘了好多好多的莲蓬（其实，出去也是可以买的，但是没有自己摘有意思）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">竟然在芦苇丛里发现了鸭蛋，意外之财啊。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/f67faa5d2ebc86dad7fadf95ab2e3022.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">风凉凉的，天空时不时飞过一些我叫不上名字的鸟儿，身边是好友，周围是美景，人生乐事，也不过如此吧！</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/6a51ed95e190e76b3cad3726b86e64d2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">玩了两三个小时，采摘了新鲜的莲蓬，又偷偷地摘了几个美丽的大荷花，打道回府了。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">回去后，老板娘早已备好早餐，我们又狼吞虎咽地解决了！美滋滋滴…</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">吃完饭已经10点多了，带上我的咸鸭蛋、我的小篓子还有我的莲蓬一起回家咯。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/65d930def7b4938881dd991ef1041a84.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">反正对于白洋淀的美我已经黔驴技穷了，任何一张照片都无法表达出我对白洋淀深深的爱，各位还是来亲自体验一番吧。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">温馨小提示：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">1.一定要提前联系接送和住宿，最好非周末去避免扎堆。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">2.一定不要理会半路拉客的黑导游，你会被宰得哭晕在厕所。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">3.白洋淀蚊子比较多，一定要注意防蚊，建议自带一些防蚊药。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">4.没来过的自驾游的朋友，要注意，进村之后gps不太好用，最好是和接客的人电话联系。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">5、若不想开车，可做汽车或是火车道白洋淀：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">到石家庄运河桥客运站，乘汽车到安新客运站（票价50），距白洋淀旅游码头3公里左右，出站后可乘出租车到旅游码头；</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">或者乘高铁到白洋淀站（快），出站后坐16路公交，可到达离码头1公里处，再步行到达码头。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">​<br/></span></p>',NULL,'1467266068','1467277241','4','','','',NULL,'',NULL,'16',NULL,NULL,'','1',NULL,'','...','0','','','10','0','83');-- <xjx> --
INSERT INTO `sline_article` VALUES
('47','0','45','只需25块钱就能够看得到的绝美之地','','','','飒飒','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/c787077fd87803ce7e913ed33639147c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">早就听朋友们说封龙山景色引人入胜，文化历史遗迹众多，关键是离得近。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">只是俗事缠身、无缘光顾，恰巧雨过天晴、气温不高，临时决定云游封龙山胜景，也算了却我的小游心愿。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">俗语说：“山不在高，有仙则名；水不在深，有龙则灵。”虽然封龙山的海拔只有800米，跟泰山啊、黄山啊这些名山比起来差远了，但它也有自己独特的美，对于周边的市民来说绝对是一个休闲避暑的好去处。</span></p><p></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p></section></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">为了尽可能避免太阳毒晒，早上八点开车从小区出发，一路上车少、人少，越往前山越多。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">比起市里浑浊的空气来说，这里的空气清新多了，氧气吸得多了，人也兴奋起来了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">半个多小时的时间就到了山脚下，山门前有个挺大的停车场，一辆车才5块钱，够便宜的吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/1bad42ade8277ec8a80de281d7ccbd80.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">封龙山大门前，有一棵柿子树，听停车场大爷说，这里原来是种满树的斜坡，在平整门前地时，特意留下了这一棵</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/be8c4b92b0f30c446d96be50ab1d1eec.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">进到山门里，左侧是一座“大公庙”，大公庙是唐太宗李世民为封龙山义士张大宏而建的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/5e0486bcc93e7ff475d26d7de84524dc.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">大公庙后面有一块“飞来石”，感觉好多山上都会有一个飞来石。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/3aabddc7c5bc3fb9004b414431c92c70.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">封龙山登起来并不难，山路不陡，更像是散步，路边有好多树，挺凉快。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">离入口不远有一个亭子跟很大的鱼池，鱼池里有很多金鱼，好多人都在这里喂鱼。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/bded0f73465cd981bbde93350ddd0182.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">旁边还有秋千，坐在上面，吹着小风，看着小鱼儿，简直是舒服的不要不要的</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/f01ed7201c6240d71a09844ec85883bd.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">一路上都是缓缓而上的台阶，爬起来一点也不费劲</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/80c92350770ae0d35544c80d9840ece9.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">加上路边的各种野花，感觉整个路程都很轻松。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/eb4b2a23eeaf6d21cb20453f83fb1b69.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">再往前走，就到小瀑布了，这里的水还算是比较多的，靠近水边明显能感觉到凉快</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/f67dc9fb7d70905f9d63f5c73e26a00f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/f460439272dfe3cbe1d8e70198ab10e2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">继续往前走，刚刚还在感慨，这山也太没有挑战性了，忽然间就陡起来了，不过跟抱犊寨什么的比起来，小菜一碟了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/b4b16146ae6facc8516f1fed84b8b43b.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">这会儿就快要到山顶了，看见这个牌子了不，看到这个牌子就是看到了希望，冲啊！！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/f88227471888134dbd4cb3473ef22980.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">卯足劲，一口气爬到了山顶，著名的百草寺和封龙书院都在山顶上。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">山顶上有卖吃的，无外乎烧饼、方便面、凉皮之类的，实在饿可以考虑来一点，不然我还是建议你下山回市里吃吧。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">个人感觉百草寺没啥太大的意思，封龙书院倒是可以逛一逛。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/0d38f8ee0598c4adabb1341d2105f015.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">一进书院，书香气息扑鼻，好像回到了读书的时候。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">进门不远就是一个状元楼，登上状元楼，过一把状元的瘾。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/42180ec01f3dcf606038c0d42763b9e8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">整个书院并不是一马平川，而是根据山势起伏建成的，有高有低、曲折回转，每一个建筑都很精致，古香古色。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/e0e1723f85dcc25bdd37ae842731209c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">进去之后突然就不敢大声说话，怕影响到书院的宁静气氛。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/892c80f524bc9236ef038ef5317854f2.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">跟现在的学校相比，书院面积并不大，但是放在以前就算是大的了，况且是建在山顶上，工程量很大的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">有山有水，有小桥。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/86b20d1919de406100dfca770087f0ad.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/b078a0f7d0bfee98962f67d3132acb6a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/9d7798d2aeb92baa437a89c8cbcb6c69.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">竟然还有洗墨池。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/43aad028556af6be237917a38242708c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">突然间，想到了梁山伯祝英台，虽然故事不是发生在这里，但是看到书院就想到了他们。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">从书院出来，不远处有一个孤零零的白色亭子，好像是新建好的，反正也不觉得累，就走过去看看吧。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/4493d38d440bb5584ca92e68f4abf17f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">好吧，没啥意思，就只有一个亭子，视野还算比较开阔。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">返回的时候突然看见了滑翔伞，这里竟然还可以玩滑翔伞，觉得不是十分安全，还是算了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/3970263c3a2f6fb3ca142bbb72b6b696.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">下山的时候选择的是另外一条道路，相比上山来说下山的路线有些陡，但完全可以接受。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/cc5a315610dad72652856433408bfa3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">​<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/e3695d4a5a4109246ff17194a3acaeeb.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">途中碰到一对老夫妻，年龄得有70岁了，两人拄着拐杖在爬山，一直听到老爷爷在讲书院的故事，看来是很了解书院的历史了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">偶遇一只小松鼠，好想把你带回家~~</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/3aa6e624f52d53b1199e4b0df0a7ee7e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">越走越累，越走越慢，边走边休息。好不容易到山脚了，如释重负。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">山门前的停车场上现在已经停了好多车，远没有了早上来那会的安静，吵吵闹闹的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">我的封龙山之旅就这样结束了，下次有时间还会再来的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br/></p><p></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"391\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 1.5em 1em 1em; pa