: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">◆全程距离：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">约15公里</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.3906px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">◆</span>乘车指示：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">从解放广场乘坐游2路，车票3元，直达。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.3906px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">◆</span>自驾线路：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">石铜路—铜冶—封龙山。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p></p>','/uploads/2016/0701/c787077fd87803ce7e913ed33639147c.jpg','1467266803','1467343770','29','','','',NULL,'',NULL,'16',NULL,NULL,'','0',NULL,'','...','0','','','10','0','83');-- <xjx> --
INSERT INTO `sline_article` VALUES
('48','0','46','惊险 刺激！现实版的盗墓笔记竟发生在……','','','','飒飒','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0701/8d290f73beb703dea9aa2c8d0a63012e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">10年那会儿，《唐山大地震》上映，我在苦逼兮兮地上着大学。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">不记得具体细节，只记得哭得稀里哗啦，记得片尾那长长的刻满金色字的纪念墙，还有骑车子的老人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/6c49fcc47e5606ecf0d99a8d960d0386.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">16年，恰逢唐山大地震40周年，也正好赶上世界园艺博览会在唐山举办。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">就这么决定了，去唐山，看一下那涅槃重生的奇迹！</span></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85694\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section class=\"layout\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"layout\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; padding: 0px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); text-align: left; width: 550px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; min-height: 32px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline-block; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-top-style: solid; border-top-width: 1px; color: inherit; display: inline-block; width: 72px; font-size: 18px;\">写在前面</span></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">由于时间有限，出发前狠狠做了一番攻略，想完成一次完美的唐山自驾游。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">DAY1 :&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">唐山地震遗址纪念公园——世园会</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">DAY2：</span></span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">清东陵</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">住宿、门票都是提前在网上定好的，省了很大的麻烦。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;\">大概行程就是这些了，中间的小插曲、小故事请大家慢慢往下看。</span></p></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85694\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section class=\"layout\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"layout\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; padding: 0px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); text-align: left; width: 550px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; min-height: 32px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline-block; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-top-style: solid; border-top-width: 1px; color: inherit; display: inline-block; width: 64px; font-size: 18px;\">怎 么 走</span></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">石家庄到唐山大约有450公里的距离，开车需要五个小时。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">我个人的自驾路线（仅供参考），表嫌弃！黄石高速——新元高速——京港澳高速——荣乌高速——京沪高速——滨保高速——长深高速——唐津高速——唐海线。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/531899d5961395aae81855bee1e173ad.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">从唐山市区到遵化清东陵大约80多公里的路程，开车一个多小时就够了，详细路线下文有介绍，实在不懂问度娘！</span></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86586\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85694\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section class=\"layout\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"layout\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; padding: 0px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); width: 538px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; min-height: 32px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline-block; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-top-style: solid; border-top-width: 1px; color: inherit; display: inline-block; width: 64px; font-size: 18px;\">住 哪 儿</span></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">唐山住的地方可多啦，既有高端大气上档次的香格里拉大酒店、万达洲际酒店，也有各种品牌的连锁酒店，如果喜欢民宿的话，还可以体验到当地的特色民宿。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">去之前，我们在网上提前预定了梅苑快捷酒店(唐山卫国路店)，208块钱一个晚上，标间，含有双人早餐。</span></p></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">地理位置那叫一个好，就在市中心，出门南行便可到达世园会、纪念公园等景点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/8fb803c7857371a510e8377f9888a073.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">但，酒店的早餐有点差劲，就不多做评论了，不挑的话能填饱肚子，你要是对吃十分讲究的话，我还是劝你别去尝试了，不然会毁掉你一天的好心情滴。</span></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85694\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section class=\"layout\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"layout\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; padding: 0px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); text-align: left; width: 550px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; min-height: 32px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline-block; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-top-style: solid; border-top-width: 1px; color: inherit; display: inline-block; width: 72px; font-size: 18px;\">具体行程</span></section></section></section></section></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"39\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" placeholder=\"请输入标题\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; height: 36px; display: inline-block; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold; line-height: 36px; float: left; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\">第一天</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; height: 36px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 9px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-right-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; border-top-width: 18px !important; border-top-style: solid !important; border-top-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-width: 18px !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">只有两天的游玩时间，只能牺牲宝贵的睡眠了，早上4:30起床，5点已经在路上了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">还好现在是夏天，出门的时候天已经大亮了。路上车很少，也许大家都还在和周公约会呢。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/30a7d1617761cfc5022cc368149a69b4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">之所以选择自驾出行，是因为喜欢在高速公路上飞奔的感觉，看着房子、树木在身边掠过，好像全世界都被自己甩在身后…这个时候必须听许巍和朴树的歌！哈哈哈~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/405c67db4662eb25b9cf70da8cc90e2a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">由于起的太早，我的专用司机“李先生”太困了，不得已在服务区休息了一会儿，吃了点东西。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">满血满魔，原地复活，继续上路。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">下高速跟着导航找酒店，在百货大楼附近找到了酒店，到酒店已经接近中午11点了。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">还好，路上没堵车~~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">据说，这栋百货大楼，是唐山的地标性建筑！方方正正的一栋房子……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/5f8dfac2dd5082130c42f6d743640de9.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">酒店地理位置优越得也是没谁了，心中窃喜啊。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">停车，搬行李，上楼，环境比想象中的要好许多，暖暖的色调，给人很温馨的感觉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/ccb0ed2ffd83d8ef1dedb3c093123b1e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">放下行李，想着出去琢磨点吃的，我唯一能想到的和唐山有关系的吃的就是糖炒栗子。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">但，总不能让我买一包栗子作为午饭吧！况且我也不喜欢。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">听到我们讨论吃的，前台小妹告诉我们，附近有个川骄自助火锅，还不错，下楼就能看见。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">立马上网团购，53一个人，随便吃。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">美味而又营养的菌汤锅底，色香味俱全，oh my love!。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/06bc882a6312208110fa507d8842e30c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">吃完饭，大约1点多一点，直接去唐山地震遗址纪念公园。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">从酒店出发到公园，大约10分钟的车程，直走、右转就到了，很好找的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">下图中的红色路线为实际行走的路线，A点为酒店位置。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/2cc6b1c8449c63c93a582a4eb1c78ce4.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">一到公园门口就被这座石钟震撼了，这一刻将永远留在我们心中！！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">纪念公园是免费的，不需要买票，但要凭借身份证、学生证等才可进去。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">所以，各位一定要带好身份证啊！！！</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/1ba2818aa7f090bb3e75ed96aadf7ee3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">不知为什么，一走进公园里心情就好沉重，刚才的愉悦一扫而光。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">公园广场正前方的纪念水池，告诫我们要同舟共济。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/05b0f4d9a6f0482b80c069124260e8d4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">广场的左侧则是长长的纪念墙。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">记得在看那部电影的时候，最触动我的就是这面墙。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">这个夏天，时隔六年，我终于真正站到了它的面前。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/a83d9ce2126fd71868df7e4b789b0dbe.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">很震撼的地方！当面对那一个个名字的时候，悲凉感油然而生。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">再往里走，是地震遗址区，残破的现状、惨不忍睹。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/97bf1f7a575c63f08eeafba91a0593a1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/9d3f5986bc836a73f00d8a7026b7661c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">本来计划好好参观一下这个公园的，但是越看心情越沉重、越悲伤。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">估计再待下去我脆弱的小心灵会受不了的，所以只在里边待了大约一个小时的时间就出来了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">给我一分钟的时间，容我缓缓。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">公园的西边就是世园会，两个景点紧挨着，看地图就很清楚了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/158b4628513ddfa269e33a6f059c9df5.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">Ready?Go!</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">先来一张copy的图，瞅瞅，多气派！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/e27b42ddb2d6c17d76fb15bf3b684cde.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">特地下午过来，就是为了赶世园会的夜场（晚上九点关门）。来之前在网上订的门票，两张才156块钱，包含夜场，可直接待到晚上九点！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">门口有票贩子卖100块钱一张（正价120一张），真实性不得而知，自己想象去吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">园内有观光车，10元钱一张票，能坐两次。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">对于看重点或体力不支的朋友来说是很好的选择。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/99558484dd04dc0f1e791cc6c25d3a1c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">世园会共有六个门，但特别有意思的是，六个门的位置不是通常的按序号1、2、3排列，而是呈跳跃式分布，不知设计师脑子里想些个啥。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">最早见到的是一号门，问了一下，他们说我们的票只能从六号门进入，围着车道开了很久才到六号门，六号门门口有个挺大的停车场。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">本来2点多就从纪念公园出来了，光转悠着找门口、停车、取票、排队就花了半个多钟头。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">等进到园内，都快3点了，急死我了，只能走马观花了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/88513672f5b83c801cc49b9fa1d37cf3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">门票类似公交卡，刷卡进入，需两道安检，不许带打火机。那烟瘾犯了咋办？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">从六号门进入，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">一进门就能看见粉色的房子，类似糖果屋。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">远远望着那粉刷成粉色的楼，想象着里面有售琳琅满目的糖果。结果走进一看，进馆需要收费……</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">我这颗向往的心刹那间碎的xi~sei~xi~sei……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/592678942ba1760bbbfccda1ff68d41f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">以六号门为原点，逆时针游览，往2号门的方向走，途经国际园。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/90ecada4fc4f769e7cc9c8c29e20edc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">典型欧美风格建筑，国际园的展区连成一片，我都不知道步入哪个国家了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/cd30e03ae7010b6e18b1ab2efc2c7380.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">国际园忒大，有些园区根本没有进去……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/cbcc506104e8bf9d867ad3cf6cf1e473.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">没进去也好，据说里边好多卖东西的，有的卖日本、韩国的婴儿用品、面膜等，有的卖外国的一些零食，有的甚至卖中国的东西，呵呵~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">离开国际园，我们往2号门（生态科教园方向）出发。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">好喜欢这种河中绿洲。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/510351d6a271b4baf61a3f36f1d1f458.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">生态科教园占地面积非常大，但貌似并没有完全开发好，或者说，并不能吸引像我这样的游客的兴趣，一路走的很快。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/712dd80d8b82f8cf6216e380ba9844e8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">从2号门往4号门方向，这条路确实很长，而且除了湖景，没有其它景点（地图上可以看到），这一段最好坐车，此处可省略好几万步。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">途路过少儿世博园、低碳生活馆、低碳生活园等景点，没兴趣。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">路边拍摄的小花花，很漂酿，有木有？！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/028068f0fd45960ee2a43b7fbcf7b0d1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">四号门附近的龙山，看着挺高，实际爬上去不累，可以“一览众山小”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/3b58a9eecc832007b59ca057ee7363a3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">下山，继续往前，到达国内园，一眼就瞅见了岭南园，典型的江南style。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/dfb50c34cfeb9d87aabae9e73ff0571c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/adb4f75784de0d9af6bb129ada87d2af.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">我大帝都——北京</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/cc8851db8081fc092b7b7fa6b2ffe34b.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">张家口——距离2022冬奥会精确到秒的倒计时（拍的不清楚，见谅）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/95ec0cd3874b4242596ff7fd05cb0cae.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">沧州的铁狮子，我想到了红烧狮子头，哈哈哈</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/2a017f9de26bb2f42cd9eaa2fef8ebd8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">快看,红彤彤的国际庄</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/188c99ff8bda6a7d2843b76e6a62f805.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">本来挺期待台湾文化园的，结果却有点小失望，里面都是卖东西的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">有一个台湾人卖面膜25元/帖，买4赠1，想想还是有些小贵，没有买。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">他给我们看了他的身份证，台湾人的身份证正反面都是信息，配偶的姓名也记录在上面。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">涨姿势了哦！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/ffba79b6dd82a8c28b988ebdb16a7eea.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">出国内园，继续前行到达一号门。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">夕阳下的世园会，有点小壮观哈~~</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/e0f5e1e5a588bffa464f1759af3bf42c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">到丹</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">凤朝阳广场已经是晚上了，盗用一张白天的图片。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/1feda3bb968d7c61ef3be80943ced07b.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">夜晚下的喷泉，这也是夜游世园会中最值得看的了，白天喷泉也是有开放的，但是效果没有夜景好。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">黑白对比图，还是晚上的喷泉有feel！！！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/dd559c958863286fed71199559b4bb5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/5df7dc030d7ecda7b872d0a1a462ea19.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">再来一张夜景图，不记得在哪里拍了，只是觉得好漂酿~~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/5f12ca99a364b6c637dddb44464e65ec.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">走马观花地转了一圈，赶到9点关门之前回到了六号门。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">宝宝好累，但是又好满足！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">上一张百货大楼的夜景结束今天的行程，累得不想吃饭。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/37c8de0867b959e683cb06d3458665f9.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">回酒店，来碗泡面做夜宵，这酸爽！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">对于苦逼穷游一族来说，泡面和旅行那是绝配！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/66547fc3606803339b0c4c34f19bca3c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"39\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" placeholder=\"请输入标题\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; height: 36px; display: inline-block; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold; line-height: 36px; float: left; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);\">第二天</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; height: 36px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 9px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-right-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; border-top-width: 18px !important; border-top-style: solid !important; border-top-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-width: 18px !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">早上醒来已经七点半，穿衣、洗漱、收拾东西、吃饭、退房，八点四十从酒店一路向北开往清东陵。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">十点左右到达清东陵，一路上风景不错，清东陵不愧是块风水宝地啊，怪不得当年皇帝选择此地呢。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/72cee79f29775ec981dd9065c897aa8b.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">清东陵门票正价152块钱，我们来之前从网上买的，135元，包含景区内的观光车！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">到景区之后人不多，私家车车可以直接开进去，所以就没有乘坐景区的观光车，早知道就不买带观光车的票了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/f7474371244db606f8476169b7b42599.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">里边只有靠近慈禧墓的那一块停车要收10块钱，其它地方好像都是免费停车。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">景区特别大，每个陵墓都特分散，由于时间有限，我们没有挨个游览，只看了几个有代表性的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/21175e9c71acd4587f3d3ee5bf132639.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">沿以前皇帝祭祀时的路线进入整个陵区， 先看到清东陵总门户 “石牌坊”，高大威武。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/7c4dbd522d1ad8ae550f8d28da47c4a1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">开车经石牌坊、大红门、龙凤门直奔清东陵内最大的地宫——裕陵，乾隆皇帝的陵寝。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/e36a8b030470557e5c55dace4db27de7.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">乾隆地宫里刻满了各种经咒，我读书少，看不懂。至今，也有很多砖家解释不了其中的含义。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/0ed7129813ea15659797fd31c30bf567.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">不过，砖家说了，其中的文字百分之百都是吉祥经咒，并没有传说中的黑暗诅咒。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/84999b0ace95e8b3e3e4f3f36e063f78.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">这张光线好一点~</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">地宫石刻如此，可以想象好大喜功的乾隆皇帝棺内的珍宝之巨，可惜被盗了，只能靠想象咯。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/84b6f50dacfd55619e706431f1cc4d74.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">从裕陵出来向前走便是裕妃园寝，是葬乾隆妃子的地方。乾隆<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">活得时间长，老婆自然也就多一些。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/5a6e5be12164f4928a0ec54b3c14a66b.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">《还珠格格》里边的皇后和香妃就葬在此。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">裕妃陵园之所以开放，我想很有可能是电视剧《还珠格格》的功劳。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">记得当时最出名的一句台词就是“香妃娘娘变成蝴蝶飞走了”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/ffc46b16be0d1a1411adab3933571611.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">出来后，途经后花园去孝陵。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">棱恩殿后大门封闭，进不去了，据说，顺治皇帝地宫完好无损，未被偷盗。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">大幸啊，出家的传说和简朴陪葬品成了庇护，看来低调些还是很对滴。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">所以说啊，千万别炫富！不怕贼偷，就怕贼惦记！！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/e4b988be015afda014c8b1e0b8d195f4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">顺治皇帝神位</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/b71cc2a24f80f6f60d0787a1a63fe849.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">顺治出家塑像</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/d9864fbe0e3b79c786759362ebdf290d.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">出孝陵，返回到定东陵。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">定东陵有两座，分别是慈安和慈禧的，慈安陵不开放，当然了，还是因为慈禧老佛爷的名气大！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/b1aff5f4bcd30a9ce3e3444da7d685e7.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">慈禧的小碑楼</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/9ecacd8e4be3035725195ef919ca055e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">慈禧太后陵墓殿前的陛石，“凤在上，龙在下”，制式很是奇特</span>！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/23ce25cabc7b092e11df4ba9eb7b2aba.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">虽然经过了被盗的洗劫，但还能够感觉到那曾经的奢华。慈禧太后的炫富，最终招来了一群盗贼啊!</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">天花板都要描金的，真有钱！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/416a101e4156fb5413a156c79dc32142.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">当时的盗墓者们只看到了金银珠宝，却忽略了慈禧的这条被子，这可是用金线做的，多奢侈。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/6b462b7507edcd072a8cde825be7b295.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">转完这几个陵墓已接近下午两点，皇家陵园果然是大大大大啊，生前享尽世间繁荣，死后还要这么隆重。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">此情此景，不由想大声呐喊“吾皇万岁万岁万万岁”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/f5ebef38542ab63952eb46471254b41e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">不在此感慨了，还是吃点东西抓紧时间上路吧，回家要补习一下历史知识。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px;\">到家已经八点半，好累！想想还要早起上班，头疼，赶紧洗洗碎吧！</span></span></p><p><br/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; -webkit-border-image: url(http://remote.wx135.com/img/stats.gif);\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85559\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section class=\"layout\" style=\"margin: 30px auto 0px; padding: 0px 10px 5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(194, 201, 42); box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 15px; background-color: rgb(194, 201, 42);\"><section style=\"margin: -5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(121, 123, 170);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">行前准备</strong></span></section><section class=\"135brush\" data-style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 10px; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(194, 201, 42); box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 15px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(194, 201, 42); box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">1、</span></em><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">准备好钱，现金、银行卡啥的，穷游可不是什么好玩的事情。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">2、</span></em><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">出门旅行一定要带上自己的身份证，如果有学生证、军官证、教师证、老年证、导游证也要带上，有些景区门票是可以优惠哒。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">3、</span></em><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">出门之前看看天气预报，天冷就多带厚衣服，天热就注意防晒、防中暑，下雨记得带雨衣、雨伞。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">4、</span></em><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">必备物品：相机、电池、内存卡、充电器、常用应急药品等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 25.6px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">但，</span></em></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">最重要的就是要带上一颗充满好奇的心，这样你和你的小伙伴才会有一段美好的旅程。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(194, 201, 42); box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p></section>','/uploads/2016/0701/8d290f73beb703dea9aa2c8d0a63012e.jpg','1467267305','1467334949','28','','','',NULL,'',NULL,'16',NULL,NULL,'','0',NULL,'','...','0','','','10','0','84');-- <xjx> --
INSERT INTO `sline_article` VALUES
('49','0','47','这只\"鸡\" 出名了！快来看~','','','','','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">鸡鸣山，位于河北省张家口市的一座山峰。此山孤峰独秀，高高耸立在河北省张家口市下的花园东侧2公里左右的地方，跟张家口市距离约为50公里。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/1d5345c5c982f7bf157a6587e469a5db.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">刘元震《游鸡鸣山记》：“或曰昔山有金鸡鸣而群鸡皆鸣焉。或曰唐代崔智韬逐化虎之妇至此闻鸡鸣，故名焉。”</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/201bae3760dd30f154f67d8e9b6faf2a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">巍峨峥嵘，郁郁葱葱。雄伟的山，神奇的山，富有灵性的山，我想如此说它定不夸张。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/cf3607c2435486cfd500c67808ef5b8c.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">它是一座有故事的山峰，在十多亿年前，发生了一次大地震，却推挫而成造就了海拔1128.9米占地17.5平方公里的它。</span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/0228f75aea17dae7fdd1587d0b3dacd3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">大自然是个艺术家在它身上展现的淋漓尽致。它还有很多别名。由于它山势突兀，草木繁茂，孤峰插云，秀丽壮观，故有“参天一柱”之称。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/90d9eac0d9e04a8d53b5b0732c90c075.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">它气势壮观，历史悠久，景色优美，文化底蕴深厚，所以还被誉为塞外小泰山。那现在就让我们一起走进鸡鸣山，用心享受它给予的完美体验吧。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/a721485122731a30b814502d40a5f9c2.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">山门牌坊，四柱三门，如其对联所写“知水仁山地，风光霁月天，青山做主人，好鸟为朋友。”乐山乐水者，可欣然前往。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/612e9b6a0609cbac59ce5943fc5b7fab.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">人物花卉，鸟兽鱼虫，生动美观。不身临其境永远也无法体会它的奇特之处。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/c680727fef618a01922eae56082bf86c.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24px;\">在避风桥上，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">即使外面狂风大作，只要登上它，一下子就没有了一点风声，万籁俱静，风都汇入桥洞钻出，一丝一缕也没有越过桥面。如此神奇之地，世间少有。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/ad4a319e60b77f223559529a1c478160.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">转眼又来到光明塔，若你是宗教的信徒，那么带着你的信仰来到此地绝对不会让你失望。在这里蕴藏。登顶然后眺望四周美景，完全是一场视觉的盛宴。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/9e9a513feb8816b7e54c740b3f139465.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">在这个聒噪的时代，我们总向往来一次心灵的栖息。而这里云水禅心，千年流转。</span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/322a543b6a65516b02a0784c0d74a5e0.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">可远观远山碧水，近观佛影禅林，风能为你洗涤岁月的尘埃，景能给你清澈如水的宁静，让你暂时忘记五味杂陈的烟火。那么风光无限好，何不下花园呢?</span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/b1511eb9377862fc0ba1eebfc1863d70.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">旅游攻略</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px;\">景区开放时间：8:40-17:00</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px;\">景区门票信息：门市价:60.0RMB起 成人票60元，儿童票40元，亲子（2+1）160元，亲子（1+1）100元。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">如何到达</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px;\">1、从石家庄自驾、坐火车或者汽车前往张家口市。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px;\">