('51','0','49','快围观~康熙皇帝在这砸了个华丽丽的大坑！','','','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 23.2727px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"3238\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section class=\"layout\" style=\"margin: 2em auto 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px rgb(255, 129, 36); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"135brush\" style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 28px solid rgb(255, 129, 36); color: rgb(255, 129, 36); line-height: 1.4; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">这里叫将军泡子，据史书记载当年康熙皇帝亲征，这里是击溃漠西葛尔丹叛军的地方，葛尔丹率兵打到了塞罕坝，布下了由几万峰骆驼组成的骆驼阵，清军的大炮万炮齐鸣，惊散了骆驼，强烈的震动改变了此地的地理结构，致使地下水涌出形成了一个大泡子。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85850\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 2px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em; line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: inherit; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/0c21f648c974b1b468e1f5729773ae0f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: inherit; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">这里的水面开阔，四面环山，拍晚霞照片的最佳地点，水中的芦苇长得一丛丛的，而且还错落有致，好像是给摄影师安排的道具。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: -1px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;\"><br/></p></section></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85850\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 2px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em; line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: inherit; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/900d042c66f5cfeb7b7a56627045bb54.jpg\"