建筑，将千年北方文化融汇进这座古城。</span></p></section></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: -1px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\"></section></section></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 23.2727px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85850\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 2px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em; line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 1em; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/35ecf95fd09979c7779ca8b6969e6c4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; color: inherit; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">古城环城水系古城最休闲、最适合发呆的地方，游人们可以三五成群地相约与此细细品味，品尝香茗的同时，沉醉在柔软的时光当中。</span></p></section></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: -1px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\"></section></section></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 23.2727px;\"><section class=\"135edit