ing: 0px; line-height: 23.2727px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85912\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); transform: rotate(0.01deg);\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 15px; width: 556.364px; color: rgb(110, 156, 40); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(229, 243, 208);\"><span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.2727px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">顺着她手指着的方向望去，茫茫一片花海...</span></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top-width: 1em; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); border-top-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); height: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; border-left-width: 1em !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-right-width: 1em !important; border-right-style: solid !important; border-right-color: transparent !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mBOu3McmTlj9zO0aedO2MSRicVPh22o09WV5PopADIssdWRDBibOmAXicuaVdiaPYx4uKVfwsJ9caocg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-ratio=\"NaN\" data-w=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/IBtzVgbte9mBOu3McmTlj9zO0aedO2MSRicVPh22o09WV5PopADIssdWRDBibOmAXicuaVdiaPYx4uKVfwsJ9caocg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-ratio=\"NaN\" data-w=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/62eda18bee1c5ef7363d54eaa758e5eb.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p></section><p></p><p></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.2727px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85912\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); transform: rotate(0.01deg);\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 15px; width: 556.364px; color: rgb(110, 156, 40); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(229, 243, 208);\"><span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">几匹骏马在小丘上吃草，几头奶牛在山坡下舒懒地躺着，偶尔听到马的几声嘶鸣。茫茫草原被这些牲畜点缀的生趣盎然。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top-width: 1em; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); border-top-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); height: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; border-left-width: 1em !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-right-width: 1em !important; border-right-style: solid !important; border-right-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/95ba66bfd4424f325e69df43380da9f8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p></section></section><p></p><p></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85912\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 23.2727px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); transform: rotate(0.01deg);\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 15px; width: 556.364px; color: rgb(110, 156, 40); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(229, 243, 208);\"><span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">看着那无际的草原如同一幅巨大的画铺展在天地间，绿得那么纯粹，绿得那么渺远，真得无法用语言来形容。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top-width: 1em; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); border-top-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); height: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; border-left-width: 1em !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-right-width: 1em !important; border-right-style: solid !important; border-right-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/09bf0f8d4b07b61012c9c99519e0f75a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p></section><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85912\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 23.2727px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); transform: rotate(0.01deg);\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 15px; width: 556.364px; color: rgb(110, 156, 40); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(229, 243, 208);\"><span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">沿着曲折蜿蜒的牧道，沿着舒缓悠扬的马头琴音，穿过岁月的河流，穿越历史的烟尘，让人心驰神往，魂牵梦萦。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top-width: 1em; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); border-top-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); height: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; border-left-width: 1em !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-right-width: 1em !important; border-right-style: solid !important; border-right-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/a22782fb8e35d4e82099f055c6b3ab85.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85912\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); transform: rotate(0.01deg);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 15px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; width: 556.364px; color: rgb(110, 156, 40); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(229, 243, 208);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.2727px;\">天穹压落，云欲擦肩。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top-width: 1em; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); border-top-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); height: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; border-left-width: 1em !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-right-width: 1em !important; border-right-style: solid !important; border-right-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/dd7eed31b15b43cd0806cb4f47178884.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p></section></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85912\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.2727px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); transform: rotate(0.01deg);\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 15px; width: 556.364px; color: rgb(110, 156, 40); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(229, 243, 208);\"><span class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">琥珀色的阳光温暖而晴柔，一碧万顷的草色铺开绿绸般的绒毯，在他的身后连绵逶迤，与遥远的地平线挽手相连。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top-width: 1em; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); border-top-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); height: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; border-left-width: 1em !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-right-width: 1em !important; border-right-style: solid !important; border-right-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/9d02e818b39d5fe65b0ecf91010ebb1d.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p></section><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 23.2727px;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"85912\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); transform: rotate(0.01deg);\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 15px; width: 556.364px; color: rgb(110, 156, 40); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(229, 243, 208);\">下了山坡，坐在草地上近距离闻着花香，不想时间过的太快。仿佛我们都变成了孩子，没有任何的顾忌。</section><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; border-top-width: 1em; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); border-top-color: rgb(229, 243, 208); height: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; border-left-width: 1em !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-right-width: 1em !important; border-right-style: solid !important; border-right-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0630/b9efb25beafb0171ac5ce484162ba2e5.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</p><section class=\"article135\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"2490\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none;\"><section class=\"layout\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 3px solid rgb(229, 243, 208); box-sizing: border-box;\"><section data-bcless=\"lighten\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\">来到草原总有一种让人心旷神怡的感觉，你是不是也想来这里吹吹风，骑骑马，放松下心情呢？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">自驾时长</strong>：约7小时</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">自驾路程</strong>：约600公里</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">自驾线路</strong>：石家庄-京昆高速-张承高速-金莲川</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; text-align: center; line-height: 23.2727px;\">周边住宿</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; text-align: center; line-height: 23.2727px;\">：快捷酒店、农家院（人均约100元）</span></p><p style=\"margi